,"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34269,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/17\/dua-between-two-sujood\/","url_meta":{"origin":4962,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Supplication between the two prostrations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 17, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, used to say between the two prostrations, \u201cO Allah, forgive me, have mercy on me, restore me, guide me, and provide for me.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 284 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36721,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/07\/27\/allah-guide-yahud\/","url_meta":{"origin":4962,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sneezing: Response to a non-Muslim who sneezes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Jews used to sneeze in front of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, hoping that he would say, \u201cMay Allah have mercy on you.\u201d The Prophet would say, \u201cMay Allah guide you and amend your affairs.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2739 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25557,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/06\/mercy-believers-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":4962,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Curses: O Allah, have mercy on believers I cursed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 6, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I am only a human being. Whenever I scold, curse, or punish a Muslim man, then turn it into purification and mercy for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6361, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2601 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2027,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/01\/mercy-forgiveness-bedouin\/","url_meta":{"origin":4962,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Rahmah: The Prophet\u2019s forbearance with a bedouin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A bedouin entered the mosque of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, while the Prophet was sitting. The man prayed, and when finished, he said, \u201cO Allah, have mercy upon me and Muhammad and no one else.\u201d The Prophet turned to him and he said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/10\/04\/not-sent-to-curse\/","url_meta":{"origin":4962,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: The Prophet not sent to invoke curses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Kariz ibn Samah reported: He was part of a delegation sent to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and it was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, pray against the tribe of \u2018Amir.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cI was not sent to invoke curses.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 19\/189 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35558,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/05\/hayy-qayyum-rahmatik\/","url_meta":{"origin":4962,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek help by the Merciful, the Living","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 5, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, whenever he encountered a difficult matter, he would say, \u201cO Living, O Sustaining! By Your mercy, I seek deliverance!\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3524 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/w